<div>
<p>
<persName>劉謙</persName>
<pc>，</pc>字<name key="劉謙" type="zi">漢宗</name>
<pc>，</pc>開封人<pc>。</pc>少補衛士<pc>，</pc>數遷至捧日右廂<term>都指揮使</term>
<pc>，</pc>領嘉州<term>團練使</term>兼京城巡檢<pc>。</pc>元昊反<pc>，</pc>改<placeName>博州</placeName>
<term>團練使</term>
<pc>、</pc>
<placeName>環慶路</placeName>馬步軍總管兼知<placeName>邠州</placeName>
<pc>。</pc>
