</div>
<div>
<p>
<name key="範恪" type="givenName">恪</name>有弓勝<num value="1">一</num>石<num value="7">七</num>鬥<pc>，</pc>其箭鏃如鏵<pc>，</pc>名曰鏵弓<pc>。</pc>又於羽間識其官稱<pc>、</pc>姓氏<pc>，</pc>凡所發必中<pc>，</pc>至<num value="1">一</num>箭貫<measure quantity="2" unit="people">
<num value="2">二</num>人</measure>
<pc>。</pc>他日<pc>，</pc>取蕉蒿砦歸<pc>，</pc>
